<p>test perfo DMA sync/async:</p>

<p>ASYNC</p>

<p>64 bytes =&gt; 235¬µs</p>

<p>SYNC</p>

<p>1 =&gt; 51
64 =&gt; 51
512 =&gt; 136
1024 =&gt; 136
2048 =&gt; 136
4096 =&gt; 136
8192 =&gt; 136</p>

<p>Lecture FIFO = lent
5.5¬µs par byte.
Ce qui limite la bande passante MAX multivoies √† 1.4Mbps</p>
